      <title>法国巴黎银行的 Boutle 认为市场反弹将扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/bnp-s-boutle-sees-market-rally-broadening-out-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行美国股票和衍生品策略主管 Greg Boutle 认为，市场反弹将从一些超大市值公司扩展到更具周期性的经济领域。他正在接受“彭博监测”节目采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/bnp-s-boutle-sees-market-rally-broadening-out-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:55:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德通过 HPS 交易进军私人信贷领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/blackrock-elbows-into-private-credit-arena-with-hps-deal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Sridhar Natarajan 在“彭博未平仓合约”中表示，贝莱德公司曾被认为在私人市场表现不佳，但随着收购 HPS Investment Partners 成为信贷行业的一股力量，该公司正在摆脱这一污名。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/blackrock-elbows-into-private-credit-arena-with-hps-deal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:54:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stifel 的 Piegza 预计美联储将在 12 月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/stifel-s-piegza-expects-fed-to-cut-rates-in-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stifel 首席经济学家 Lindsey Piegza 预计美联储将在 12 月降息，然后在 2025 年再降息三次。在“彭博监测”节目中，Piegza 表示美联储尚未“扼杀”通胀。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/stifel-s-piegza-expects-fed-to-cut-rates-in-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:47:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德收购 HPS 有何意义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/why-blackrock-buying-hps-makes-sense-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德将以全股票交易的方式收购 HPS Investment Partners，交易价值约为 120 亿美元。Sridhar Natarajan 将在“彭博未平仓合约”中提供更多内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-03/why-blackrock-buying-hps-makes-sense-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资金逃离穷国，世界银行呼吁减免债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/world-bank-calls-for-debt-relief-as-funds-flee-poor-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行首席经济学家呼吁私人贷款机构承担最贫穷国家部分债务减免成本，因为创纪录的高额还款耗尽了本应用于医疗、教育和基础设施的预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/world-bank-calls-for-debt-relief-as-funds-flee-poor-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软件公司 ServiceTitan 寻求通过 IPO 筹集高达 5.02 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/software-startup-servicetitan-seeks-to-raise-502-million-in-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[家庭服务软件公司 ServiceTitan Inc. 正寻求通过首次公开募股筹集高达 5.016 亿美元的资金，这可能是 2024 年美国最后一次重大上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/software-startup-servicetitan-seeks-to-raise-502-million-in-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德以 120 亿美元全股票交易收购信贷公司 HPS</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/blackrock-to-buy-credit-firm-hps-in-12-billion-all-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司同意以全股票交易的方式收购 HPS Investment Partners，交易价值约为 120 亿美元，此次收购将推动这家全球最大的资产管理公司跻身私人信贷领域最高排名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/blackrock-to-buy-credit-firm-hps-in-12-billion-all-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银因骚扰举报人面临法国刑事审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/ubs-faces-criminal-trial-in-france-for-harassing-whistleblowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团在巴黎接受审判，被指控骚扰两名举报人，举报人揭露了该银行帮助法国富人逃税的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/ubs-faces-criminal-trial-in-france-for-harassing-whistleblowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 11:40:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因担心关税，许多中国铜贸易商暂停进口美国废铜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/many-china-copper-traders-halt-us-scrap-imports-on-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京安泰科信息发展有限公司称，由于预计唐纳德·特朗普就任总统后将征收关税，许多中国金属进口商已停止购买美国废铜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/many-china-copper-traders-halt-us-scrap-imports-on-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 04:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
